gomodel:SYNGO_4516  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: The electron micrograph (Fig. 2A) of MFC layer 2/3 at P18 shows immunogold labeling of Neurocan near the plasma membrane adjacent to a spine (Sp) and axon terminal.\nFig 2D shows Neurocan labeling adjacent to axon terminals (AT) at P18.\nFig. 2E depicts Neurocan labeling at neck of spine (Sp) and near excitatory synapses at P80.\n\nThe antibody specificity is confirmed in Fig. 2F.. Experimental description: \"C57BL/6 WT mice (P18 and P80) were anesthetized and perfused transcardially with phosphate buffer...\" p.2" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0269-0311" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9377-7414" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9880-1214" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9681-3318" ;
        dc:date           "2021-01-28" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_4516" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10090" .

